    "description": "<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/4b2ec5552fdfe9211f980c381e83df39.poster.avif?t=1704407165\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/4b2ec5552fdfe9211f980c381e83df39.webm?t=1704407165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>射击、摧毁、收集、制造，然后再摧毁更多！《Dark Gravity》是一款快节奏、低多边形垂直射击游戏，提供非线性战役模式，有大量敌人和首领。制造新武器，升级你的飞行器，打造一架终极空中战争机器！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/ce75a7c46bc7a79da089dc0d29790509.poster.avif?t=1704407165\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/ce75a7c46bc7a79da089dc0d29790509.webm?t=1704407165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>第五次世界大战后，世界迎来了和平。十多年来，大联盟一直通过扼杀一切潜在危险来引导人类走向更美好的未来。然而，最近，有一个无法忽视的新威胁的嫌疑。<br><br>作为SAF部队的一员，你的任务是夺回被未知叛乱分子占领的Shielton基地。没有人知道他们是谁，他们想要什么。更糟糕的是，即使IMC部队也无法通过其先进的武器从基地驱逐他们。那是来自另一个世界的武器。但是...这些叛乱者是主要威胁吗？难道背后没有更大的事情吗？没有时间提问！你必须不惜一切代价阻止他们！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/3b0008eede50e07a544d323b4bd64baf.poster.avif?t=1704407165\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/3b0008eede50e07a544d323b4bd64baf.webm?t=1704407165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>游戏机制非常简单 - 摧毁所有敌人，尽量避免每颗子弹...至少是可以避免的子弹。你的特殊机动允许你躲避普通抛射物。即使被击中，你只会失去一个额外的武器！然而，要小心强大的首领！他们可以用他们的终极无法躲避的攻击将你撕成碎片！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/be8569cc26a6d53e01b6d6f8a948c4b4.poster.avif?t=1704407165\" width=610 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1776590/extras/be8569cc26a6d53e01b6d6f8a948c4b4.webm?t=1704407165\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
